des: Learn digital marketing tips from basic tips to trending topics with Misty. Misty Buck, president of Miss Ink, LLC, has over 15 years of experience in the marketing industry with over a decade as the principal of the award-winning Internet marketing agency in Miami. Her clear and concise marketing counsel is sought-after by both companies and professionals that seek to keep their brand fresh, visible, relevant, and ahead-of-the-game.
